data.name: ReadCase
data.value: select distinct T1.NUMB, T1.CSE_OPEN_DATE, T1.PA_MEDICAL_SERVICE, T1.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID from CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.NUMB > @numb) and (T1.NUMB between cast(@caseNumber1 as char(10)) and cast(@caseNumber2 as char(10))) and (T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_I_NUMBER) and (T2.KS_CASE_IND = 'Y') order by T1.NUMB

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select IDENTIFIER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, KS_CASE_IND, CAS_I_NUMBER, COUNTRY, TRIBAL_AGENCY from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST with(readuncommitted) where (KS_CASE_IND = 'Y') and (@casINumber = CAS_I_NUMBER)

data.name: ReadInterstateRequestHistory
data.value: select top(1) INT_GENERATED_ID, CREATED_TSTAMP, ACTION_CODE, FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO, TRANSACTION_DATE, ACTION_REASON_CODE from CKT_INT_RQST_HIST with(readuncommitted) where (@intGeneratedId = INT_GENERATED_ID) and ( ( (FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO in ('ENF', 'EST', 'PAT')) and (ACTION_CODE = 'R') ) or ( (ACTION_CODE = ' ') and (FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO = ' ') and (ACTION_REASON_CODE = 'OICNV') ) ) order by CREATED_TSTAMP

data.name: ReadInterstateRequestHistoryInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) T1.INT_GENERATED_ID, T1.CREATED_TSTAMP, T1.ACTION_CODE, T1.FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO, T1.TRANSACTION_DATE, T1.ACTION_REASON_CODE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.KS_CASE_IND, T2.CAS_I_NUMBER, T2.COUNTRY, T2.TRIBAL_AGENCY from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_INT_RQST_HIST T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.IDENTIFIER = T1.INT_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.KS_CASE_IND = 'Y') and (@casINumber = T2.CAS_I_NUMBER) and ( ( (T1.FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO in ('ENF', 'EST', 'PAT')) and (T1.ACTION_CODE = 'R') ) or ( (T1.ACTION_CODE = ' ') and (T1.FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO = ' ') and (T1.ACTION_REASON_CODE = 'OICNV') ) ) order by T1.CREATED_TSTAMP
